  <brief_title>Wound Healing and Pain Management in Partial Thickness Burns</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pain Management and Wound Healing in Partial Thickness Burn: Comparative, Post Marketing, Observational Trail Comparing Advanced Foam Dressings to Conventional Treatment.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
